<plot>Another of the Mentone Brevity shorts made for Universal Pictures distribution that highlights the song and dance vaudeville team of Smith &amp; Dale (Joe Smith and Charlie Dale), who started as a blackface act in 1898, appeared in films as late as 1951, and served as the role models for "The Sunshine Boys." Virginia Verrill, Jeanne McCully and Ferry Corwey also on hand to contribute their specialities.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?206729</url></doc>
